  "texts": [
    "Upload Image: The user uploads a geo-tagged image.",
    "Extract Geo-tagged Locations: The exchangeable image file format (Exif) decryption algorithm is used to extract the geo-tagged locations from the uploaded image.",
    "Feature Extraction: The image is then processed for feature extraction using the VGGNet16 CNN model which is trained with a customized dataset.",
    "Tune Extracted Features: The features extracted from the image are then fine-tuned with the trained weights of the LSTM algorithm.",
    "Generate Raw Headline: The output of the LSTM is a raw headline that describes the image in a basic way."
